definition: to carry/to convey/to load/to hold/to fill up/and/also/as well as/simultaneously
to record in writing/to carry (i.e. publish in a newspaper etc)/Taiwan pr. [zai4]/year

sentences.english: A new reentry guidance algorithm for RLV(reusable launching vehicle) is presented.
sentences.chinese: 提出了一种针对可重复使用运载器的再入制导算法。

sentences.english: Ridership was about 60% of what it was in 2009.
sentences.chinese: 地铁运载的乘客总数约为2009年的60%。

sentences.english: Thellos merchant shellop was convoyed by a destroyer.
sentences.chinese: 这艘运载货物的船由一摈除舰护航。

sentences.english: These satellites will go as piggyback on PSLV's (Polar Satellite Launch Vehicle), officials said.
sentences.chinese: 有官员称，这些卫星将搭乘印度的极轨卫星运载火箭。

sentences.english: An aqueous caustic solution removes carrier gas impurities harmful to the detector cell.
sentences.chinese: 苛性堿溶液去除运载气体中对检测元件有害的杂质。

sentences.english: The stellar wind carries ever less mass at ever increasing speed.
sentences.chinese: 恒星风所运载出的质量愈来愈少，使其速度愈来愈快。

sentences.english: For carrier rockets, however, the technique of lateral separation design is normally used.
sentences.chinese: 而运载火箭通常采用横向分离式设计技术。

sentences.english: As there were not enough life-boats for everybody.
sentences.chinese: 没有足够的救生艇运载所有乘客。

sentences.english: Weighting of radwaste machines is a necessary procedure.
sentences.chinese: 对运载着放射性废料的卡车的称重是个必要的过程。

sentences.english: A stately bridge carried over the turbulent water by a boat?
sentences.chinese: 一座庄严的大桥由一只船运载着穿过狂暴的海洋？

sentences.english: The simulation elements of the vehicle will be destroyed on impact with the water.
sentences.chinese: 这些运载工具上的模拟元件如果进水将会被毁灭。

sentences.english: But the craft will also carry a number of student-designed experiments.
sentences.chinese: 这颗卫星还将运载一些学生设计的实验。

sentences.english: The space rocket carries a satellite as a payload .
sentences.chinese: 这枚宇宙火箭运载了两颗卫星。

sentences.english: The long- term day carries the ability as 100.
sentences.chinese: 远期日运载能力为100万人次。

sentences.english: Nor are aircraft the only vehicles from which destructive electromagnetic pulses can be launched.
sentences.chinese: 飞行器亦非唯一可发射破坏性电磁脉冲的运载工具。

sentences.english: When the fire reached the cargo of chemicals the whole ship went up.
sentences.chinese: 火焰延伸到运载的化学品时，全船都爆炸了。

definition: to carry a passenger/(of spaceships etc) manned/also pr. [zai3 ren2]
